Agwaetiti El Nabatat ma ọ bụ Agwaetiti Kitchener, (Geziret En Nabatat (Plant Island) ma ọ bụ Botanical Island) Ọ bụ obere agwaetiti oval dị na Naịl na Aswan,  Ijipt. Ọ na-erughị otu kilomita n'ogologo na obosara ya erughị 1/2 otu kilomita
Ogige Aswan Botanical dị n'àgwàetiti ahụ.
Agwaetiti El Nabatat bụ otu n'ime agwaetiti abụọ kachasị na Naịl dị nso na Wan, nke ọzọ bụ Elephantine.
Elephantine bụ nke buru ibu, ọ dịkwa n'etiti El Nabatat Island na obodo Aswan (n'akụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ)
Ya mere, ọ nwere ike isi ike ịhụ obere agwaetiti El Nabatat site na Aswan: "Aswan na-apụ n'anya n'azụ Elephantine Island".

A na-akpọbu agwaetiti a dị ka Kitchener's Island, nke aha ya bụ Lord Kitchener bụ onye nwe ya.
E nyere ya agwaetiti ahụ, mgbe ọ jere ozi dị ka Consul-General na Egypt site na 29 Septemba 1911 ruo June 1914.

Site n'enyemaka nke Ministry of Irrigation, Kitchener gbanwere obere agwaetiti ahụ dị mita 750 (2,460 ) n'ogologo ka ọ bụrụ paradaịs nke osisi ndị dị iche iche, ọtụtụ sitere na India, na osisi ndị dị n'ogige nwere ụzọ ndị a na-ahụ anya. O mechara banye n'ihe onwunwe nke gọọmentị Ijipt ma jiri ya mee ihe dị ka ụlọ nyocha a na-akpọ Botanical Research Institute, Aswân Botanic Island.
Àgwàetiti ahụ, n'ozuzu ya, mejupụtara Aswan Botanical Garden

Mmadụ nwere ike ịhụ ọtụtụ ụdị osisi na osisi ndị dị n'okpuru okpomọkụ, ndị dị iche iche, na ndị a na-adịghị ahụkebe dịka osisi Royal Palm na osisi Sabal Palm. Lord Kitchener malitere nchịkọta ahụ ma lekọta ya kemgbe ahụ. Ogige ndị ahụ na-ewu ewu n'etiti ndị obodo na ndị njem nleta, dị ka ebe ị ga-aga maka ehihie dị jụụ site na mkpọtụ nke obodo ahụ, na maka picnic izu ụka
Nke Felucca nwere ike iru agwaetiti na ubi nke ruru akụkụ ndịda ọwụwa anyanwụ nke obere agwaetiti ahụ
